#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn23.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamamāravagga "
msgstr "1. About Māra "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Dutiyachandarāgasutta "
msgstr "10. Desire and Greed (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn23.10:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.10:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ rādhaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "When Venerable Rādha was seated to one side, the Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.10:1.3"
msgid "“rūpe kho, rādha, yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha. "
msgstr "“Rādha, you should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for form; and any attraction, grasping, mental fixation, insistence, and underlying tendencies. "

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.4"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ anabhāvaṅkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhammaṃ. "
msgstr "Thus that form will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.10:1.5"
msgid "Vedanāya yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha. "
msgstr "You should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for feeling … "

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ sā vedanā pahīnā bhavissati ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṅkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.7"
msgid "Saññāya … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.8"
msgid "saṅkhāresu yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha. "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.9"
msgid "Evaṃ te saṅkhārā pahīnā bhavissanti ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṅkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.10"
msgid "Viññāṇe yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha. "
msgstr "consciousness; and any attraction, grasping, mental fixation, insistence, and underlying tendencies. "

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.11"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ viññāṇaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ anabhāvaṅkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhamman”ti. "
msgstr "Thus that consciousness will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.10:1.12"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.10:1.13"
msgid "Rādhasaṃyuttassa paṭhamamāravaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn23.10:2.1"
msgid "Māro satto bhavanetti, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.10:2.2"
msgid "pariññeyyā samaṇā duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.10:2.3"
msgid "Sotāpanno arahā ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn23.10:2.4"
msgid "chandarāgāpare duveti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
